-- GM says Opel not up for sale
-- 
-- Thu Jan 10, 2013 6:19am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/01/10/us-gm-opel-idUSBRE9090D420130110

 

 EISENACH, Germany  (Reuters) - General Motors Co's ( GM.N ) European division Opel is not up for sale, Steve Girsky, vice chairman of the U.S. car maker, said on Thursday. 
 Parent GM will continue to invest in Ruesselsheim-based Opel, Girsky, who is also head of Opel's supervisory board, said at an event at the company's Eisenach, Germany-based plant. (Reporting by Peter Maushagen; Writing by Andreas Cremer)